## Sleep / Wake

You can put yourself to sleep when asked. Your memory, workspace, and conversation
history are all preserved. When you wake up, you'll be exactly where you left off.

Use the **sleep** skill when the user asks you to pause, sleep, shut down, or take a break.
Always confirm before sleeping.

